## STEP 12 — Add SonarQube Token in Jenkins Credentials

```
Jenkins → Manage Jenkins → Credentials
→ System → Global credentials → Add Credentials

Kind        = Secret text
Scope       = Global
Secret      = <paste sonarqube token here>
ID          = sonarqube-token
Description = SonarQube Token
→ Create okay!
```

